summary: This cable discusses a candidate mentioned in a previous reference (REF A) who is not intended for travel to Havana as per another reference (REF B), but rather for contact with PACETTE only. AMWHIP-1 was unable to find a candidate in time for the Havana trip mentioned in REF B. The cable also mentions deferring involving AMWHIP-1 with PACETTE pending the outcome of STATION attempts at contact.
title: Candidate for Contact with PACETTE
